This book likely addresses the critical role of company culture and personal branding in the success of a business.

## **10\. Lean In by Sheryl Sandberg**

<YouTubeEmbed videoid='-NK28iM41bw' params='controls=0' />

Initially aimed at empowering women in the workplace, its principles of leadership and resilience are universally applicable to all entrepreneurs.

